HEADWORD: Finfoot
<hw>Fin"foot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
South American bird (<spn>Heliornis fulica</spn>) allied to the grebes.
The name is also applied to several related species of the genus
<gen>Podica</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
